{"title":"Combined feed","url":"https://leoshcn.github.io/feeds/all.xml","elements":[{"title":"Makeship (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <b><a href=\"/wiki/Makeship\" title=\"Makeship\">Makeship</a></b> produced a plush toy of Wikipedia's 25th-anniversary mascot <i>(pictured)</i><span style=\"padding-left:0.15em;\">?</span>","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Makeship","retrieved":1773987034950},{"title":"Sudjarwo Tjondronegoro (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <b><a href=\"/wiki/Sudjarwo_Tjondronegoro\" title=\"Sudjarwo Tjondronegoro\">Sudjarwo Tjondronegoro</a></b> advanced <a href=\"/wiki/West_New_Guinea_dispute\" title=\"West New Guinea dispute\">Indonesia's claim to Western New Guinea</a> in the United Nations, and later accepted control over the territory?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sudjarwo_Tjondronegoro","retrieved":1773987034951},{"title":"The Patriot's Progress (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <a href=\"/wiki/Henry_Williamson\" title=\"Henry Williamson\">Henry Williamson</a> stopped writing <i><b><a href=\"/wiki/The_Patriot%27s_Progress\" title=\"The Patriot's Progress\">The Patriot's Progress</a></b></i> for a year because he was so disgusted by the praise for <i><a href=\"/wiki/All_Quiet_on_the_Western_Front\" title=\"All Quiet on the Western Front\">All Quiet on the Western Front</a></i><span style=\"padding-left:0.15em;\">?</span>","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Patriot%27s_Progress","retrieved":1773987034952},{"title":"Kwek Leng Beng (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <b><a href=\"/wiki/Kwek_Leng_Beng\" title=\"Kwek Leng Beng\">Kwek Leng Beng</a></b> was gifted a gold-dipped <span class=\"nowrap\">AK-47</span> by <a href=\"/wiki/Al_Waleed_bin_Talal_Al_Saud\" title=\"Al Waleed bin Talal Al Saud\">Al Waleed bin Talal Al Saud</a> after they jointly purchased the <a href=\"/wiki/Plaza_Hotel\" title=\"Plaza Hotel\">Plaza Hotel</a> from Donald Trump?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kwek_Leng_Beng","retrieved":1773987034998},{"title":"formal semantics (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <b><a href=\"/wiki/Formal_semantics_(natural_language)\" title=\"Formal semantics (natural language)\">formal semantics</a></b> uses logic and mathematics to study language?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Formal_semantics_(natural_language)","retrieved":1773987035000},{"title":"Cobb (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that Lee Blessing called his baseball play <i><b><a href=\"/wiki/Cobb_(play)\" title=\"Cobb (play)\">Cobb</a></b></i> a \"one-man play for four men\"?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cobb_(play)","retrieved":1773987035000},{"title":"James Stanley Rogers (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that <b><a href=\"/wiki/James_Stanley_Rogers\" title=\"James Stanley Rogers\">James Stanley Rogers</a></b> was the secretary of a panel that oversaw the production of optical munitions in Australia during the Second World War?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/James_Stanley_Rogers","retrieved":1773987035001},{"title":"K50 Waterfall (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that Vietnam's <b><a href=\"/wiki/K50_Waterfall\" title=\"K50 Waterfall\">K50 Waterfall</a></b> is named after its height?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/K50_Waterfall","retrieved":1773987035013},{"title":"Mohongo-class gunboats (Wikipedia — did you know?)","contents":"... that the seven <b><a href=\"/wiki/Mohongo-class_gunboat\" title=\"Mohongo-class gunboat\"><i>Mohongo</i>-class gunboats</a></b> were uncharacteristically comfortable?","link":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mohongo-class_gunboat","retrieved":1773987035014},{"title":"Destination of the Month (Wikivoyage recommendations)","contents":"<style data-mw-deduplicate=\"TemplateStyles:r4523569\" typeof=\"mw:Extension/templatestyles mw:Transclusion\" about=\"#mwt7\" data-mw=\"{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;templatestyles&quot;,&quot;attrs&quot;:{&quot;src&quot;: